  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His activities are making no impact here at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, if you don't remember who Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stresemann is, ask your sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She, she will know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the reason why she said that-- I thought about this, and I-- at first I didn't know, was there really a Mr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stresemann in, in Waldorf, or did she mean something else?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and, of course, my sister was no longer alive so many years later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then it came to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stresemann was, of course, a chancellor of, of, of Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I looked up some of the things he had done, I found that he had, that he had won-- in the Weimer Republic-- that he had won the Nobel Peace Prize for his efforts with the League of Nations and in trying to, to establish peace.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my mother's way of letting us know that here it was '38, the time when Neville Chamberlain went to Munich and made, made his peace overtures, to let us know that absolutely no one was paying any attention to what he was trying to do within Germany.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When did you enter the military?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in November of 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I, I was drafted, since I, I couldn't volunteer, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] technically being considered an enemy alien.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which also meant that I couldn't own a camera or have a, a shortwave band on my radio.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But other than that, there were no, no real restrictions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it-- because there were no distinctions made between Jews and ordinary Germans, I simply fell into that category.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so-- but they did eventually get around to me, and so I was drafted.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
